From Mike Mychalkiw Subject Re Cobra Locks Greetings netters Steve writes about Cobra Locks Well I have the mother of all On Friday the of April I took possesion of a ' Cobra Links lock This was a special I weighs a I had to carry it home and it was digging into my shoulder after about two I have currently a Kryptonite Rock Lock through the front wheel a HD padlock for the steering lock a Master padlock to lock the cover to two front spokes and the Cobra Links through the rear swing arm and around a post in an underground parking Next Friday the I have an appointment to have an alarm installed on me When I travel the Cobra Links and the cover and padlock stay at By the I also removed the plastic mesh that is on the Cobra Links and encased the lock from end to end using bicycle inner tubes two of them I got the from bicycle dealer that sold me the Cobra The guys were really great and didn't mark up the price of the lock much and the inner tubes were FXSTC Rock 'N Roll Mike Mychalkiw HOG Ryerson Polytechnical Institute DoD Just THIS side of Academic Computing Information Centre doh Just the OTHER EMAIL